data.description: Super Cute updated home in Debeque! 3bed 2bath home with an office that has been updated throughout! New interior paint, new flooring and carpet, updated bathrooms, New electric fireplace, all new kitchen appliances, new island, farmhouse sink and backsplash! Multiple outbuildings/sheds! True RV parking with clean-out and electric and water hookups! Cellar roof was also reinforced and new shelves built! Come see it for yourself!
